lead_paragraph: Bradley Wright-Phillips scored twice, Sacha Kljestan had a goal and two assists and the New York Red Bulls beat New York City FC 4-1 on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Wright-Phillips, Kljestan Lead Red Bulls Past NYCFC 4-1
